World of the Wild - Episode 5: The American Prairies | Wildlife Documentary

Watch 'World of the Wild - Episode 6' here: https://youtu.be/SyuMC8iDX_0

This episode explores the wildlife of the great American prairies.

World of the Wild is a more profound journey into the crucial, fragile interdependence between animal life and the environment. Guided by the most up-to-date research we travel through jungles, forests, mountain ranges, deserts, and oceans to discover animals, their habitats, and the environment that sustains them. Their behavior, and ability to develop, survive and adapt to a changing climate are evident.
